    "abstractNote": "\"From the writings of St. Ephrem it is so very clear that he was a very prayerful man, although he did not leave any treatise, not even a small one, on prayer. [...] In his poetical writings Ephrem has left many prayers of his own. One of them [\"Hymni 87 de Fide\" (52, 15)] with particular emphasis on Christian unity prompted me to write this paper.\" (pp. 47-48)",
